    \dfrac{14}{39}-\dfrac{2}{3}\lambda-\dfrac{7}{13}\lambda+\lambda^2-\dfrac{6}{39}&=0 \\[5pt]
    14-26\lambda-21\lambda+39\lambda^2-6&=0 \\[5pt]
    &\hspace{-2.3cm}\tcbhighmath{39\lambda^2-47\lambda+8 = 0} 
    \end{align*}
    $$

  - 
    $$
